OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with coastal showers
OL,6,Fpushing inland across East Anglia
OL,7,Fthrough much of the day. Brighter
OL,8,Fconditions to be found further west,
OL,9,Fwhere the occasional bright or sunny
OL,10,Fspell develops through the afternoon.
OL,11,FFeeling cool, particularly along
OL,12,Fcoasts in northeasterly winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloud and showers across East
OL,15,FAnglia persist into the night, easing
OL,16,Foff through the early hours. Elsewhere
OL,17,Fa cold night with clear spells leading
OL,18,Fto a rural frost developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
